OL,3,CYoung people on benefits to be offered
OL,4,Cconstruction, care and hospitality work
OL,6,FYoung people on benefits will be
OL,7,Foffered job opportunities in
OL,8,Fconstruction and hospitality in an
OL,9,Feffort to halt the rise in youth
OL,10,Funemployment.
OL,12,FMinisters have announced an #820
OL,13,Fmillion package aimed at helping
OL,14,Falmost one million people get off
OL,15,Fbenefits and into work.
OL,17,FThe funding includes training and work
OL,18,Fexperience in construction,
OL,19,Fhospitality, and health and social
OL,20,Fcare for 350,000 young people on
OL,21,Funiversal credit.
