OL,3,CYoung people on benefits to be offered
OL,4,Cconstruction, care and hospitality work
OL,6,FOthers will be offered "intensive
OL,7,Fsupport" to help them find work, while
OL,8,Fup to 55,000 young people will be
OL,9,Foffered guaranteed, government-backed
OL,10,Fjobs from spring 2026.
OL,12,FBut those who refuse to engage with
OL,13,Fthe help on offer without a good
OL,14,Freason could lose some of their
OL,15,Fbenefits.
OL,17,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,18,FMcFadden said: "Every young person
OL,19,Fdeserves a fair chance to succeed.
OL,20,FWhen given the right support and
OL,21,Fopportunities, they will grasp them."
