OL,3,CYoung people on benefits to be offered
OL,4,Cconstruction, care and hospitality work
OL,6,FThe extra funding comes amid a rise in
OL,7,F"Neets", 16-24-year-olds not in
OL,8,Femployment, education or training.
OL,10,FSome 940,000 young people are now
OL,11,Fconsidered Neet, a rise of 195,000 in
OL,12,Fthe last two years, driven mainly by
OL,13,Fincreasing rates of sickness and
OL,14,Fdisability.
OL,16,FAnd the Resolution Foundation has
OL,17,Fwarned that the figure is on course to
OL,18,Freach one million for the first time
OL,19,Fsince the aftermath of the financial
OL,20,Fcrisis, when it peaked at 1.2 million
OL,21,Fin 2012.
