OL,3,CYoung people on benefits to be offered
OL,4,Cconstruction, care and hospitality work
OL,6,FWriting in the Sunday Mirror,
OL,7,FEducation Secretary Bridget Phillipson
OL,8,Fsaid: "One in eight young people are
OL,9,Flocked out of learning and work.
OL,10,FThat's nearly a million futures on
OL,11,Fhold, a colossal waste of young talent.
OL,13,F"We need more early intervention.
OL,14,FThat's why we're creating a
OL,15,Fstrengthened Risk of Neet Indicator,
OL,16,Fas part of an #820 million investment,
OL,17,Fan early warning system that spots
OL,18,Fwhere young people may need support
OL,19,Fbefore damage sets in.
