OL,6,F"We're piloting automatic enrolment in
OL,7,Ffurther education, creating almost
OL,8,F300,000 new skills opportunities for
OL,9,Fthose on Universal Credit, and
OL,10,Fexpanding Youth Hubs to every local
OL,11,Farea ` offering everything from CV
OL,12,Ftips to mental health support.
OL,14,F"But we know we can't fix this issue
OL,15,Fwithout tackling the poverty that
OL,16,Ffeeds it. That's why we're investing
OL,17,Fto fight the stain of child poverty."
