OL,6,FMcFadden said the new funding was "a
OL,7,Fdownpayment on young people's futures
OL,8,Fand the future of the country,
OL,9,Fcreating real pathways into good jobs
OL,10,Fand providing work experience, skills
OL,11,Ftraining and guaranteed employment".
OL,13,FFurther plans for young people are
OL,14,Fexpected to be set out in the coming
OL,15,Fweek as the Government prepares to
OL,16,Fpublish its national youth strategy.
