OL,6,FConservative shadow work and pensions
OL,7,Fsecretary Helen Whately said: "The
OL,8,FChancellor's tax hikes are driving up
OL,9,Fyouth unemployment, snatching a career
OL,10,Ffrom a generation of young people;
OL,11,Fthis scheme is nothing more than
OL,12,Ftaking with one hand to give with the
OL,13,Fother.
OL,15,F"This is an admission that the
OL,16,FGovernment has no plan for growth, no
OL,17,Fplan to create real jobs, and no way
OL,18,Fof measuring whether any of this money
OL,19,Fdelivers results.
